The formatting concept we use in this video we will use the same concept in all other videos as well.

We can format any element of the chart by double clicking on it for selecting it and then right click and select format
axis option

We will select the horizontal axis and the chart area and format it also we can select more object by exploring it.
after that we can see  first there is fill option from where we can give background color to the chart/object selected.
after that we can see second  there is effects option from where we can give 3D effects to the chart/object selected.
after that we can see third  there is size option from where we can change size of the chart/object selected.

